Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:33.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's 150,000 dollars?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:38.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter! After I kill these brats, don't forget\nto grab the cash on the ground, Eda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:41.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right! Don't move, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose... that's the end of negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:53.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:01.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Jodorovsky. I've encountered the enemy at Point Puskov.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:06.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Eda! It's Hotel Moscow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:09.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They've come out, nee-sama. The Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:10.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, nee-sama, let's confuse the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:18.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we start killing them, they'll return to their base.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:23.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, nii-sama. Let's split up and hunt down the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you luck, nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:27.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, nii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They lost the target in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:45.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it clearly showed the enemy who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:48.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed as if the enemy has taken our bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All units, continue your assigned tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:55.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lavochec's and Jodorovsky's squads\nhave finished the second set of orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Moving to the final location.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Discovered target two behind\NJodorovsky's squad during the retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:13.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Confirm the number of targets. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:14.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Polanski.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:19.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only target two has been sighted. I repeat, only target two has been sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:21.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Private Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming the enemy pursuing Jodorovsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:24.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can only see one as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:28.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The target is on Jodorovsky's tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We will drag it to the planned location.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So only target two has taken the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Drag that one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it know what you're doing. Those kids are pretty smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let it to believe it has the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:48.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind, and move to the next phase. Act confused and chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:53.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My subordinates will follow through in mafia style.\NPlease do not be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:57.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We will be at the park gate momentarily. Once there, we will attack the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:02.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on confusing and angering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:06.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it's angered, its senses will become dulled. That will be the turning point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:07.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:12.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant, it's time. Take command of the last squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:12.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck then, Kapitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You be careful as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:33.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,let's end this... pathetic racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:34.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect me to go back to the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:42.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We should have gone along with the trade! You're so damned greedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:43.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:49.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think saved you from having\nyour balls ripped off by Hotel Moscow?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:53.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had balls since I was born! Monkey-faced dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, you fucking bitch, draw your guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:02.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very funny, Revy. It'll be even funnier when I rip you a new asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't make a cent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:20.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Call me if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:30.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go get the car by\nmyself in the middle of a fire-fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Revy! We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do it yourself. Geez, you're not a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You cold-hearted bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for you to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:57.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to take on the both of you by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to help me with something, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:08.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get out of here after\Nnii-sama kills the Russian woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:13.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we've already killed our hosts, the Verrocchio family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:16.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass. You knew that, but you killed the boss anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Verrocchio's dead,\nthere's no reason to kill Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you continue? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:33.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You're asking why? That's... funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:39.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because we want to. There's no other reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We want to, so we do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We just want to know about our get-away driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:50.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We want someone who takes their job seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:53.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Tell me, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to hide. Come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:40.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed me. As expected of you, madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your subordinates are quite skilled as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:46.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As much as I chased them around,\NI couldn't kill a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, what shall we do, madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:53.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since I came all the way here, would you like to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:57.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About the man we killed, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:03.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A normal person would have died sooner,\nbut he lasted quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:11.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And he kept yelling out "Kapitan!\NKapitan!" until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even while bubbling so much blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're cold, madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:25.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But madame, you'll become like that man soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a shame that we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:35.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, boy, but this is the end for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:41.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, you need to apologize for your mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:42.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So go ahead and kneel right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the line for you, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:16.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you still had an ounce of sanity left,\nyou would have noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that you jumped right into the feeding grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:27.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, in the end, you're just a helpless,\nbroken, piece of shit brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you're going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:37.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:41.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to die. I can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:44.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I killed so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Many, many,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:49.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,many, many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can live for that many...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:52.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can... we can increase our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We shall never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,we're eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:05.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what your belief is? It's a very wonderful thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:13.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}"No One Lives Forever": 1980s song by Oingo Boingo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:13.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, the truth is in the song, "No One Lives Forever".\NJust like it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:19.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I could torment you before I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:23.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Considering what you did to my subordinate,\nthat would be most appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:29.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as perverse as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:34.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm just going to sit here and watch you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:40.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With that bullet wound,\nyou'll only last ten minutes at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:47.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I dedicate these last few minutes before you\nleave this world to Sahalov and Menishof.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,certain that you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:13.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry... you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:20.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:25.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant, we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:29.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was horrible, Kapitan.\NMy guts were frozen the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:30.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I made you put up with my selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:35.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kapitan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I must be getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:38.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a nice voice, doesn't she.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:40.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the voice of a psychopathic killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Her voice, at least, is the voice of an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:50.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But things sure have gone crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:51.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:57.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To think, that the gal who orchestrated the\N"night of terror" in Roanapur is our client...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still a job. Where's Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's been in a bad mood over that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:08.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, she's keeping watch outside of the cabin door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To be ready, just in case, for Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was a beautiful song. Where did you learn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:23.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I really love this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:28.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But apart from letting nii-sama hear this song...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:32.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,you're the the first, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, you seem different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:43.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like someone that's in a different place, a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:47.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I just haven't gotten used to this job yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:53.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at telling who's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Is this Balalaika?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I'm calling about, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would've called sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:10.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, do you understand what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:11.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've been paid enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because of a sense of\nobligation or attachment, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like a philanthropist?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just had to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our position depends on yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:27.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We both have things we have to do. Right, Balalaika?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, we're heading south...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:33.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Dutch. I've already prepared a few hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think I saw a few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:40.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No sorrow or regrets. Good luck, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger, Kapitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:44.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me the E-File of the Trouble List.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:47.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"E"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just a clever insurance policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:53.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Vietnam Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good answer. They're impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Hotel Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:00.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to fight them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:05.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're a torpedo boat, they're missile boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:10.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks, but the South Seas route is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about Brunei? Melody Li's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:15.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No good, pain in the ass to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:20.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the only place we can go, that's in the\nrange of this boat, is Pangkal Pinang's Elroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Bighorn" Elroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:33.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the sea. We're out at sea, but I can't even have a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:35.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you seen the ocean before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:45.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In Sicily, and at the orphanage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,all we ever saw were grey walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:53.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs24\fad(200,200)}Carpathian Mountains: eastern wing of the European Central Mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:53.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We were born in the rocky Carpathian Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was always a cloudy and lonely place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:59.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A certain dictator prohibited abortions...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,in order\nto create a work force for a poor country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if they're poor, there's no way to raise those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:10.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoned children were placed into state orphanages.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They became slaves to the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:19.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The dictator was killed. Only the orphans were left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:24.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When we were taken to Sicily,\nwe were put into blood and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:28.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We were kicked so hard that some nights\nwe couldn't stop peeing red blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I talked with my nii-sama a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:36.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Why does God make us suffer so much?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:42.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But then, nii-sama and I noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:44.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,when we were brought in front of the other children,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:51.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and had to beat another child repeatedly with a bat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the adults were all laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-sama and I were laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:17:00.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We thought, while we laughed, that this is how it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:06.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If the world will keep turning because someone is killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:10.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,that must be the reason why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:15.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To kill, be killed, and kill again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:18.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the world creates a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:23.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,sad that your brother died because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always with nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:38.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we will never die. We will always kill above this ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:42.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The world keeps existing in order to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:47.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's here and we're here. That's why we're not sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:52.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of blood, the screams, the warmth of organs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,we love it all, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:18:01.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong. The world really exists to make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:05.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. Blood and darkness are just a small part of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:12.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't cry, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:18.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've met someone as kind as you. So this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:22.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,is a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:32.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Benny! Make sure he's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:37.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:44.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, so even the likes of you still has red blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:46.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up brat, the sis isn't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:50.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed that you didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:55.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have the same smell... blood and gun smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:58.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of rotten blood and mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:19:00.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you fuck with him again, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:09.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And if you say something unpleasant to me, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:12.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Shit! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:17.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The world came together and turned them into tigers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:21.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man-eating tigers! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:24.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, don't look stuff like this in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:27.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is that kind of place. It's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll, I'll... !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to take care of that child? Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:37.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That girl can't stop killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:42.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If someone had just showed them a little\nkindness, they would have gone to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:45.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,they would have made friends and\nthey would have lived happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:49.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, that didn't happen, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:54.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So the story ends here... Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:06.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:08.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the cargo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:11.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:15.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for the rush, but did you get a passport ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:18.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I somehow managed. I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, let's meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:28.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us, with a picnic basket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:31.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:32.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:45.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:52.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was Hotel Moscow, Dutch. What else is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're done as a get-away man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My son is in South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:07.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got a letter from his wife. He's only 34, but he has already contracted cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:11.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'm tired of walking the tightrope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This was my last job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:18.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got a nice amount from Hotel Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:20.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:25.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"The sky is beautiful", right at the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:26.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:31.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, get the canvas. We've gotta cover the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:34.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need it, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:37.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine as she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:40.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Facing the blue sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:43.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,watching the sea while sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:22.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I took this job because I heard\NI could make perfect counterfeit money.
